  "title": "Provide both toggle states count",
  "body": "At the moment, we only provide the count for the current state of the toggle. A good idea from @davidpike7 is to also provide the count for the other state of the toggle.\n\nSo that you can show things like \"Only show free shipping (20)\" 20 being the number of free shipping items. It's easier to understand than \"Only show free shpping (340)\" Where 340 is the actual number of items not having free shipping.\n",
